title: Stan Lee Meets... 01-05 (2006|Digital|AnPymGold-Empire)
description:
A who's who of writers and artists help the legendary Stan Lee imagine what it would be like in this metafictional series of five one-shots. The full list includes: Stan Lee (Author), Brian Michael Bendis (Author), Joss Whedon (Author), Jeph Loeb (Author), Roy Thomas (Author), Paul Jenkins (Author), Alan Davis (Illustrator), Mark Bagley (Illustrator), Olivier Coipel (Illustrator), Michael Gaydos (Illustrator). Promotional info from the collected edition - "Celebrating the 65th anniversary of Stan Lee's employment at Marvel Comics! In five all-new 10-page tales written by "The Man" himself, Stan meets his web-slinging creation, journeys to Greenwich Villiage to catch up with his old pal Doctor Strange, is abducted to Latveria by the sinister Doctor Doom, makes the mistake of bicycling past Yancy Street and surfs the stars with a certain silver-skinned space-farer! Plus: Today's hottest writers and artists pay homage to Stan's life and career in five new 10-page stories."

This includes the following issues:
Stan Lee Meets Dr. Doom
Stan Lee Meets Dr. strange
Stan Lee Meets Spider-Man
Stan Lee Meets Silver Surfer
Stan Lee Meets The Thing

All issues are the new digital versions from AnPymGold-Empire. Thanks to them for their efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
